snippet.title: Warhammer: Vermintide 2 - Versus Open Beta | Trailer
snippet.description:
Heroes and Pactsworn!

The Beta August Test is now live! The Beta will run from August 21 to September 2nd and is open to everyone!

Learn all about the current Beta:
► https://www.vermintide.com/news/vs-bat-live-now

Learn more about Versus: 
► https://www.vermintide.com/versus

Follow our Vermintide socials
► linktr.ee/PlayVermintide
